Invocation Name: mood swing
des:
Have you ever wondered how the general population feels about any given topic? Wonder no longer. This skill finds out how Twitter feels about any topic you specify. It will tell you how Twitter felt last week, yesterday, and today on the topic.

We use state of the art machine learning text sentiment analysis to asses whether the Tweets are in general positive or negative. 50 of the most popular Tweets are gathered for each time period for the analysis.

Thanks for checking this out!
